    "body": "### Purpose\nFix some warnings of the form:\n```\nwarning #2361-D: invalid narrowing conversion from \"char\" to \"signed char\"\n        at::cuda::CUDAGuard device_guard{(char)x.get_device()};\n```\n\nFrom `rg device_guard csrc`, the standard way of doing this is:\n```\nconst at::cuda::OptionalCUDAGuard device_guard(device_of(x))\n```\nso this PR updates these spots to make them consistent.\n\n### Test Plan\nCompile vLLM kernels, look at logs\n\n### Test Result\n\n",
